<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>애니멀고</title>
</head>
<body>
{{> template/header}}
<section class="search-bar">
    <div class="search-main">지역별 동물 카페 찾기
        <div class="search-select">
            <div id="search-location-city" class="btn-group">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                    <span class="dropdown-title">지역선택</span><span class="caret"></span>
                </button>
                <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                    <li>서울</li>
                    <li>부산</li>
                    <li>대구</li>
                    <li>대전</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div id="search-location-gu">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                    <span class="dropdown-title">구</span> <span class="caret"></span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div id="search-location-name" class="input-group">
                <span class="input-group-addon" id="basic-addon1"><i class="fa fa-search fa-flip-horizontal"></i></span>
                <input type="text" id="search-location-name-input" class="form-control" placeholder="이름으로 검색하기" aria-describedby="basic-addon1">
            </div>
            <div class="search-checkbox checkbox">
                <label>
                    <input id="search-checkbox-approve" type="checkbox">
                    동물출입 가능한 카페만 찾기
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="search-result">
    <div class="search-result-bar">
        구름뜬하늘
        <div class="search-result-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-car"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-home"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-heart"></i>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cafe-result-detail">
        <ul class="cafe-result">
            <li style="background-image: url('./img/sky-1.jpg')"></li>
            <li style="background-image: url('./img/sky-2.jpg')"></li>
            <li style="background-image: url('./img/sky-3.jpg')"></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="search-result-bar-info">
        <div class="search-result-bar">
            INFORMATION
        </div>
        <div class="search-result-info">
            <ul class="cafe-info">
                <li>종류</li>
                <li>요금</li>
                <li>번호</li>
                <li>이용시간</li>
                <li>주소</li>
                <li>기타</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="cafe-info-detail">
                <li>애견카페</li>
                <li>카페음료로 계산: 7500원~</li>
                <li>02)978-4567</li>
                <li>12PM ~ 22PM 매월 셋째주 수요일 휴무</li>
                <li>홍대 어딘가</li>
                <li>주차공간이 협소하오니 대중교통을 이용하시길 권합니다.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="search-result-bar-loc">
        <div class="search-result-bar">
            LOCATION
        </div>
        <ul class="cafe-map" style="background-color: red">
            <li>MAP</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="cafe-location">
            <li class="cafe-traffic">
                대중교통
            </li>
            <li>
                <div>대중교통</div>
                <div class="cafe-loc-traffic" id="loc-traffic">
                    경의선, 공항철도 홍대입구역 7번출구
                    2호선 홍대입구역 8번출구

                    버스 273
                </div>
                <div class="cafe-loc-traffic" id="loc-car">
                    홍대입구역에서 서교동교회 방면으로 10분
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="cafe-traffic" id="car">
                자가용
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="search-result-bar-review">
        <div class="search-result-bar">
            간단 후기
        </div>
        <ul class="cafe-search-review">
            <li>A</li>
            <li>B</li>
            <li>C</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
{{> template/footer}}
</body>
</html>